        droneId - The drone modell
        location - The location
        date - The date of the flight. format: 2018-12-20
        startTime - The start time. format: 10:10:00
        endTime - the end time. format: 10:10:00
        checklistId - the id of the checklist
        flightDescription - The description of the flight.
        specialEvents - Special events that occurred during the flight
